name: CXErrorCodeNotificationServiceExtensionError.Code
desc: Constants for errors returned when reporting new, incoming VoIP calls.

items.name: case invalidClientProcess
items.desc: An error indicating that an invalid client process reported the incoming call.

items.name: case missingNotificationFilteringEntitlement
items.desc: An error indicating that the notification service extension is missing the required filtering entitlement.

items.name: case unknown
items.desc: An error that occurs when there is an unknown problem.
